&lt;p&gt;Want to work for an Outstanding Trust?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Northamptonshire Healthcare Foundation Trust (NHFT) are currently recruiting for experienced Band 5 and Band 6 Nurses&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for individuals whom have an RGN or RMN qualification wanting a rewarding career whom want to make a difference to patients and service users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are ample training opportunities within NHFT to further develop and enhance your skills and career&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; In addition to the benefits offered under the NHS terms and conditions of service, some of our nursing posts additionally attracts an incentive of £3000 pro rata for the successful applicant/s paid over the first 12 months of employment. Please refer to the attached FAQ document or contact the Recruitment team for further information. Please note incentive payments are not applicable to existing NHFT substantive staff. Terms and conditions apply.to particular areas of work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameRecruitment TeamEmail addresssmh.recruitment@nhft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
